No, I mean, from all of it,
this... this place.

1:17:35.156 --> 1:17:36.290
Man, I thought it'd be nice

1:17:36.423 --> 1:17:37.791
not to be part of the world
anymore.

1:17:39.126 --> 1:17:40.761
What do you got
against the world?

1:17:40.895 --> 1:17:42.296
It had something against us.

1:17:44.665 --> 1:17:47.168
You know,
this is the world, right?

1:17:49.837 --> 1:17:51.005
You're still in it, buddy.

1:17:52.840 --> 1:17:56.410
All he did was move
to the top of a mountain.

1:18:04.251 --> 1:18:05.252
Can you help us?

1:18:06.887 --> 1:18:08.255
Can you talk to them?

1:18:08.389 --> 1:18:10.124
Tell them
that we're good people.

1:18:13.494 --> 1:18:14.695
When I was in the Corps,

1:18:16.297 --> 1:18:17.331
during basic,

1:18:19.099 --> 1:18:22.469
they put us in a room and tossed
in percussion grenades.

1:18:22.604 --> 1:18:24.405
It was fast.

1:18:24.539 --> 1:18:25.873
You go blind.

1:18:26.006 --> 1:18:27.542
The shock wave wrecks
your inner ear

1:18:27.676 --> 1:18:29.343
so you can't stand.

1:18:29.476 --> 1:18:32.581
I saw grown men puking
their guts out

1:18:32.713 --> 1:18:34.315
till nothing but bile came out.

1:18:36.850 --> 1:18:38.018
What do you think
one of those grenades

1:18:38.152 --> 1:18:39.353
will do to a child?

1:18:49.063 --> 1:18:50.297
What do we do?

1:18:54.468 --> 1:18:58.105
Let me walk out
with the kids, today.

1:19:05.879 --> 1:19:07.147
Whose side are you on?

1:19:08.882 --> 1:19:10.217
They're coming in, Dave.

1:19:12.353 --> 1:19:15.823
I don't know when,
but this will end.

1:19:16.824 --> 1:19:18.292
But you...

1:19:18.425 --> 1:19:19.561
What, you're trying to take
my family away from me?

1:19:19.694 --> 1:19:21.228
You need to end this right.

1:19:21.362 --> 1:19:23.130
-You need to leave.
-No, not yet.

1:19:25.899 --> 1:19:28.035
Dave, stop.

1:19:29.571 --> 1:19:30.672
Riley, Dad.

1:19:30.804 --> 1:19:32.373
Baby.

1:19:32.507 --> 1:19:33.675
He's right.

1:19:33.807 --> 1:19:35.309
What are you
fucking talking about?

1:19:35.442 --> 1:19:37.244
What do you mean?

1:19:37.378 --> 1:19:38.812
You don't ever want
to see our kids again?

1:19:38.946 --> 1:19:40.548
-Is that what you want?
-Dave, stop.

1:19:40.682 --> 1:19:43.217
You think I'm some
sort of fucking joke, huh?

1:19:43.350 --> 1:19:44.151
This is my house!

1:19:44.285 --> 1:19:46.320
Ahh!

1:19:46.453 --> 1:19:48.088
Shots fired, shots fired.

1:19:49.223 --> 1:19:50.424
Get out!

1:19:51.825 --> 1:19:53.961
-Find a safe place to hide.
-Don't talk to my fucking kids.

1:19:54.094 --> 1:19:56.297
- Girls, upstairs.
- Dave.

1:19:56.430 --> 1:19:57.464
-Get out of my fucking house!
-Okay.

1:19:57.599 --> 1:19:58.832
Get out!

1:19:58.966 --> 1:20:00.901
Stay back.
Stay back from the door.

1:20:01.035 --> 1:20:02.803
Move!

1:20:02.936 --> 1:20:05.239
Get the fuck out
of my house, Eric.

1:20:09.176 --> 1:20:10.545
Argh! Fuck you!

1:20:13.947 --> 1:20:15.182
Dad.

1:20:21.155 --> 1:20:22.389
Oh, jeez! No.

1:20:23.625 --> 1:20:25.459
Alice.

1:20:25.593 --> 1:20:27.595
Hey, no, don't go,
don't go, don't go.

1:20:27.729 --> 1:20:30.964
Stay with me. Stay with me.

1:20:31.098 --> 1:20:32.534
Do you understand?

1:20:32.667 --> 1:20:34.968
Girls, come here.
Keep pressure on her.

1:20:41.442 --> 1:20:45.346
Mommy. Please. Please, please.

1:20:49.283 --> 1:20:50.851
Keep pressure on it.

1:20:55.255 --> 1:20:56.857
You don't need me anymore.

1:20:58.158 --> 1:21:00.160
You're all grown up now.

1:21:01.962 --> 1:21:03.598
Promise me that you won't leave.

1:21:05.265 --> 1:21:06.400
Promise!

1:21:08.803 --> 1:21:10.104
Promise!

1:21:11.806 --> 1:21:13.040
Promise.

1:21:30.792 --> 1:21:33.795
Get out of the way,
get out of the way, move, move.

1:21:33.961 --> 1:21:35.496
Hon, you're okay, you're okay.

1:21:35.630 --> 1:21:37.431
Riley, anything that
comes through that door,

1:21:37.565 --> 1:21:38.700
you shoot it.

1:21:38.833 --> 1:21:40.835
Do you understand me?
Do you understand me?

1:21:40.968 --> 1:21:43.137
Honey, honey, honey, honey.
Honey.

1:21:43.270 --> 1:21:45.507
Stay with me, okay?
Just stay with me.

1:21:45.640 --> 1:21:48.543
It's okay. It's okay.
It's okay.

1:21:51.746 --> 1:21:53.313
You're gonna be okay.
I promise you.

1:21:55.850 --> 1:21:57.918
<i>Mr. Hayes, is</i>
<i>everyone inside okay?</i>

1:21:58.051 --> 1:21:59.587
You shot my wife!

1:22:00.954 --> 1:22:04.358
Fuck you! Fuck you!

1:22:05.560 --> 1:22:08.530
Hold your fire.
Hold your fucking fire.

1:22:08.663 --> 1:22:11.131
Why can't you just
leave us alone?

1:22:11.265 --> 1:22:13.568
We just want to be left alone!
It's all we ever wanted!

1:22:20.107 --> 1:22:21.341
Fuck you!

1:22:25.012 --> 1:22:26.614
Dad!
We just want to be left alone.

1:22:26.748 --> 1:22:27.916
That's it.

1:22:28.048 --> 1:22:29.216
-Why can't you do that?
-Dad! Dad!

1:22:29.349 --> 1:22:30.350
What?
Stop!

1:22:30.484 --> 1:22:33.253
You want to see your mom die?

1:22:33.387 --> 1:22:34.923
They did this to her.
They shot her.

1:22:35.055 --> 1:22:37.224
They're going to come in here
and take her away from me.

1:22:37.357 --> 1:22:38.258
No.

1:22:38.392 --> 1:22:39.493
Now you shut up
and listen to me.

1:22:39.627 --> 1:22:40.795
No, you listen.

1:22:40.929 --> 1:22:42.664
You don't ever listen.

1:22:42.797 --> 1:22:44.498
All Mom ever needed was help.

1:22:45.533 --> 1:22:47.267
They didn't do this to her.

1:22:48.937 --> 1:22:50.170
You did.

1:23:23.136 --> 1:23:25.038
We'll never be a family again.

1:23:28.342 --> 1:23:30.077
This isn't home anymore.

1:23:31.713 --> 1:23:34.248
It hasn't been
for a really long time.

1:23:37.150 --> 1:23:39.353
But this place doesn't make us
a family.

1:23:41.689 --> 1:23:43.023
It never did.

1:23:49.029 --> 1:23:50.364
I'm sorry.

1:24:29.369 --> 1:24:32.840
<i>Once there was a family</i>
<i>of pioneers,</i>

1:24:34.709 --> 1:24:36.476
<i>who were looking</i>
<i>for a better life.</i>

1:24:38.412 --> 1:24:42.050
<i>There was a big sister</i>
<i>and a little sister.</i>

1:24:42.182 --> 1:24:44.217
<i>There was a mom and a dad.</i>

1:24:46.988 --> 1:24:48.756
<i>They made lots of mistakes,</i>

1:24:50.257 --> 1:24:51.859
<i>but they tried their best.</i>

1:24:56.931 --> 1:24:58.833
<i>They had a house</i>
<i>on top of a mountain.</i>

1:25:03.571 --> 1:25:06.641
<i>And they laughed and fished</i>

1:25:08.108 --> 1:25:09.644
<i>and grew their own vegetables.</i>

1:25:24.859 --> 1:25:26.694
<i>Most of the time</i>
<i>they were happy...</i>

1:25:29.463 --> 1:25:31.198
<i>except for the parts</i>
<i>that were sad.</i>

1:25:53.988 --> 1:25:55.389
<i>They weren't perfect,</i>

1:26:02.664 --> 1:26:03.931
<i>but they were a family.</i>

